					<description><![CDATA[Excellent article. In any profession where you need to write consistently, you need some form of inspiration for what you are writing. What works great on the internet are useful articles that visitor&#039;s questions, help then solve a challenge, or  help them with something actionable they can do.  As referenced above, sometimes it takes going &#039;out&#039; of the office, and getting into the head of your target audience, whether it be at a coffee shop, or hobby group, or anywhere else they hang out. Find out what people really need and want, and fill that need. You can&#039;t go wrong by doing this.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Excellent article. In any profession where you need to write consistently, you need some form of inspiration for what you are writing. What works great on the internet are useful articles that visitor&#8217;s questions, help then solve a challenge, or  help them with something actionable they can do.  As referenced above, sometimes it takes going &#8216;out&#8217; of the office, and getting into the head of your target audience, whether it be at a coffee shop, or hobby group, or anywhere else they hang out. Find out what people really need and want, and fill that need. You can&#8217;t go wrong by doing this.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
